1. First line receive days of the plunder
2. Second line receive daily plunder
3. Third line receive expected plunder
4. Calculate plunder dor all days by multiplying days*daily plunder
5. Add additional plunder every third day 0.5*daily plunder
5. Every fifth day remove 30% of total plunder
6. Check if the gained plunder reach target
7. If gained plunder is more or equal print "Ahoy ..."
8. If gained plunder is less calculate percentage left
9 Format number to 2nd decimal